person.persName: Elkanah Winne (Booneville inn keeper and Owsley County Circuit Court Clerk)

body.p: Booneville, Kentucky, inn keeper and Owsley County, Kentucky, county clerk. Virginia native. Married to Eudocia Winn. Inn keeper in Booneville in 1860. Father of William Winn. Clerk in Owsley County Court in Owsley County from 1862 to 1866.
